      <div class="msgContentFrame">This will be the new one stop thread for my Windows Gadget and Logitech LCD application.  I have created wiki articles that you can use to follow the development of these programs.  Also on those articles are discussion pages which can be used to request features as well as report bugs.  I will check them several times a week so you can expect fairly rapid support if there are issues.  These will also be the places that I update first with new releases as I finish them.  I will be locking the other threads I've created as soon as I finish typing this. <br /> <br /><a href="HTTP://ffxiv.zam.com/wiki/FFXIV_Windows_Gadget" rel="external nofollow" title="ffxiv.zam.com/wiki/FFXIV_Windows_Gadget">FFXIV Windows Gadget</a> <br /> <br /><a href="HTTP://ffxiv.zam.com/wiki/FFXIV_Logitech_LCD_App" rel="external" title="ffxiv.zam.com/wiki/FFXIV_Logitech_LCD_App">Logitech LCD App</a> <br /> <br />Thank you all for the support and kind words while I've been working on these, I hope to keep dazzling you with new features as I have time <img border="0" src="http://common.zam.com/shared/smilies/thumbsup.gif" alt="Smiley: thumbsup"/><div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><span class="sm">The greatest trick the devil ever pulled was to convince the world he didn't exist. <br /><a href="HTTP://ffxiv.zam.com/wiki/FFXIV_Windows_Gadget" rel="external nofollow" title="ffxiv.zam.com/wiki/FFXIV_Windows_Gadget">Windows 7/Vista Eorzea Gadget</a> <br /><a href="HTTP://ffxiv.zam.com/forum.html?game=268&amp;mid=128102874375645847&amp;page=1" rel="external" title="ffxiv.zam.com/forum.html?game=268&amp;mid=128102874375645847&amp;page=1">Keyboard LCD Eorzea Clock</a></span> <br /><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/356033.png" height="144" width="482" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /> <br /></div></div>
