      <div class="msgContentFrame">I solved this by simply converting to UTC times... <br /> <br /><pre>function settimers() { 
    var now = new Date(); 
    var utc = Date.UTC(now.getUTCFullYear(),now.getUTCMonth(),now.getUTCDate(),now.getUTCHours(),now.getUTCMinutes(),now.getUTCSeconds()); 
 
// Eorzea clock 
    var etime = ( ( ( utc - Date.UTC(2010, 6, 12, 16) ) ) / 1000 ) * ( 1440 / 70 ); 
    var sec = (etime % 60) | 0; 
    etime = (etime - sec) / 60; 
    var min = (etime % 60) | 0; 
    etime = (etime - min) / 60; 
    var hr = (etime % 24) | 0; 
    etime = (etime - hr) / 24; 
    var day = (etime % 32) | 0; 
    etime = (etime - day) / 32; 
    day++; 
    var month = (etime % 12) | 0; 
    etime = (etime - month) / 12; 
    month++; 
    var year = etime | 0; 
    document.getElementById(&quot;etime&quot;).innerHTML = LZ(month,2) + &quot;/&quot; + LZ(day,2) + &quot; &quot; + LZ(hr,2) + &quot;:&quot; + LZ(min,2); 
 
// Guildleve reset timer 
    var rtime = 129600 - ( ( utc - Date.UTC(2010, 9, 19) ) / 1000 ) % 129600; 
    var sec = (rtime % 60) | 0; 
    rtime -= sec; 
    rtime /= 60; 
    var min = (rtime % 60) | 0; 
    rtime -= min; 
    rtime /= 60; 
    var hr = (rtime % 24) | 0; 
    rtime -= hr; 
    document.getElementById(&quot;rtime&quot;).innerHTML = hr + &quot;h &quot; + min + &quot;m &quot; + sec + &quot;s&quot;; 
}</pre> <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Oct 20th 2010  7:44am by Tomoe </span></i><div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>World of Warcraft (I'm Inactive atm): <br /><a href="HTTP://wow.allakhazam.com/profile.html?19411" rel="external nofollow" title="wow.allakhazam.com/profile.html?19411">Omi</a> <br /> <br />Final Fantasy XI (Restarted playing on 01/08/05): <br /><a href="HTTP://ffxi.allakhazam.com/profile.xml?1588" rel="external nofollow" title="ffxi.allakhazam.com/profile.xml?1588">Omialderaan</a> <br /><a href="HTTP://ffxi.allakhazam.com/profile.xml?26938" rel="external" title="ffxi.allakhazam.com/profile.xml?26938">Omialderaan SAM</a> <br />Linkshell: <a href="HTTP://www.medics.tk" rel="external nofollow" title="www.medics.tk">Medics</a></div></div>
